Character arc template sections can include: psychological weakness, Moral Weakness, Psychological Need, Moral Need, Desire, Value of Beliefs, Problem, Opponent, Plan, Battle, Psychological Self-Revelation, Moral Self-Realization, New Equilibrium, Immoral Action, Attack by Ally (with subsection Justification), Final Action Against Opponent, Moral Decision, Initial Error, Ghost, Story World, Ally, Inciting Incident, Fake-Ally Opponeny, Revelation, Opponent's Plan and Counterattack, Apparent Defeat, Audience Revelation, Grave Gauntler & Visit to Death, Drive.
